-leak-2.jpg?resize=507,700 507w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-2.jpg?resize=768,1061 768w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-2.jpg?resize=741,1024 741w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-2.jpg?resize=1111,1536 1111w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-2.jpg?resize=1482,2048 1482w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-2.jpg?resize=253,350 253w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-2.jpg?resize=140,193 140w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-2.jpg?resize=724,1000 724w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-2.jpg?resize=150,207 150w\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-lightbox-container\"><img width=\"1754\" src=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?quality=82&amp;strip=all&amp;w=741\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-663458\" srcset=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg 1754w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=94,130 94w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=507,700 507w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=768,1061 768w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=741,1024 741w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=1111,1536 1111w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=1482,2048 1482w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=253,350 253w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=140,193 140w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=724,1000 724w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-new-leak-1.jpg?resize=150,207 150w\"></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Meanwhile, the original set more closely matches the four colors of the Pixel 9a, including pink, purple, and black and white inspired wallpapers.</p>\t<span class=\"outbrain-ad-label\">Advertisement - scroll for more content</span>\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery alignwide has-nested-images columns-4 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-lightbox-container\"><img width=\"2560\" src=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?quality=82&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1024\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-663459\" srcset=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg 2560w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=130,130 130w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=700,700 700w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=768,768 768w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=1024,1024 1024w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=1536,1536 1536w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=2048,2048 2048w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=350,350 350w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=140,140 140w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=1000,1000 1000w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=500,500 500w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=96,96 96w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-4.jpg?resize=150,150 150w\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-lightbox-container\"><img width=\"2560\" src=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?quality=82&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1024\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-663462\" srcset=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg 2560w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=130,130 130w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=700,700 700w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=768,768 768w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=1024,1024 1024w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=1536,1536 1536w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=2048,2048 2048w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=350,350 350w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=140,140 140w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=1000,1000 1000w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=500,500 500w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=96,96 96w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-3.jpg?resize=150,150 150w\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-lightbox-container\"><img width=\"2560\" src=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?quality=82&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1024\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-663460\" srcset=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg 2560w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=130,130 130w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=700,700 700w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=768,768 768w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=1024,1024 1024w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=1536,1536 1536w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=2048,2048 2048w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=350,350 350w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=140,140 140w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=1000,1000 1000w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=500,500 500w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=96,96 96w, https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2025/02/pixel-9a-wallpaper-leak-2.jpg?resize=150,150 150w\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-im